name: Volga-Dnepr Antonov An-124 "Ruslan" [RA-82081] Close Up Landing at Calgary Airport
description:
Always great to see this beast of an aircraft in Calgary, but this is my first time filming it from this angle! Here we have RA-82081, a fairly young "Ruslan" touching down on runway 17L from Sawyer International Airport in Marquette County, Michigan. ATC is included, hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
